Brookland Fine Homes is committed to building affordable homes without compromising on quality.

profile:
Let Us Build Your Dream Home in Lakeside Village...
Since 2004, Llynlea Fine Homes has established itself as Kingston's Premier Custom Home Builder.
For most people, purchasing a newly constructed home is one of the biggest financial decisions in their lifetime. The owners of Llynlea Fine Homes, John Armitage, Civil Engineer with over 40 years in the construction business, and MBA graduate Eric Davies promise to provide their customers with not only a solidly constructed house, but one their customers are proud to call "home".
Using only the very best building materials, superior sub-trades and constant communication with our customers, we are committed to delivering an unparalleled home building experience to our customers.
